Step 1:
    Trigger the zero generation alert with config "sunset" toggled      |       Verify an alert is NOT generated

Step 2:
    Trigger the zero generation alert with config "sunrise" toggled     |       Verify an alert is generated in the state "Open"

Step 3:
    Set the config "sunset" to be toggled                               |       Verify the alert state is still set to "Open"

Step 4:
    Login as the test user and acknowledge the alert                    |       Verify the alert state is set to "Acknowledged"

Step 5:
    Untrigger the zero generation alert and set the config to "Sunrise" |       Verify the alert state is set to "Closed"